Gorgeous Product! To say that the pillows and throws I ordered are gorgeous is an understatement! The quality and price cannot be beat. Our stores are in coastal communities and the items I ordered will no doubt sell very quickly! We also received them in record time giving us more time to sell and reorder this summer.

Fabulous Addition!  Beautiful quilt sets, pillows, shower curtains, and more. The perfect fit for my small coastal shop! All items received so far are high-quality (exceeding expectations), the customer service is responsive/informative, and the coastal variety is a hit with my customers. The only criticism is the overuse of box/packaging per item. However, I’ve found a creative way to recycle the influx of boxes, so I’ll be reordering very soon.

BEAUTIFUL LINENS! FIRST TIME ORDERING AND WAS VERY HAPPY WITH QUALITY OF MERCHANDISE AND REASONABLE PRICING. THE ONLY IMPROVEMENT THAT I COULD SUGGEST IS HAVING ITEMS INDIVIDUALLY PACKED IN CLEAR PACKAGING SO OUR CUSTOMERS CAN VIEW ITEMS. THEY WERE MOSTLY PACKED IN MILKY WHITE PLASTIC WHICH DID NOT ALLOW FOR VIEWING ITEMS. WE HAD TO TAKE THE TIME TO REPACKAGE EVERY ITEM.
